 <H1>Retrieving properties</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>At present, spec. defines a method called SEARCH which performs a limited search of the properties defined on a resource, and can search on the name and the value.
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Pro: allows retrieval of only specific properties
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Con: there is no way to specify a set of resources on which to perform the search -- cannot easy search a whole server (however, specifying a full-power search is really hard, and is out of scope)
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>search is an expensive operation</UL></UL></P>
